    <h1>About TalkSoon</h1>
    
    <p>Welcome to TalkSoon, your trusted partner for professional speech language pathology services in Southern Costa Rica. As a licensed Speech-Language Pathologist, I am dedicated to helping individuals of all ages overcome communication challenges and reach their full potential.</p>
    
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>We believe that every person deserves the right to communicate effectively. Our mission is to provide personalized, evidence-based speech therapy services that empower our clients to express themselves confidently and connect meaningfully with the world around them.</p>
    
    <h2>Professional Expertise</h2>
    <p>With extensive training and experience in speech-language pathology, we specialize in:</p>
    <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <li>Late talking and delayed speech development</li>
        <li>Articulation and speech clarity issues</li>
        <li>Language development and vocabulary building</li>
        <li>Autism spectrum communication support</li>
        <li>Stuttering and fluency disorders</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <p>Every client receives a comprehensive evaluation and a customized treatment plan tailored to their unique needs and goals. We use evidence-based practices combined with engaging, age-appropriate activities to make therapy both effective and enjoyable.</p>
    
    <p>Located in the beautiful Southern Zone of Costa Rica, we serve families in the region with flexible scheduling options and a warm, welcoming environment where progress happens naturally.</p>
    
